ied platinum in the US. Rolling Stone included Grace in three of its lists of the 500 greatest albums and named Buckley&#39;s version of &quot;Hallelujah&quot; one of the 500 greatest songs. In 2008, &quot;Hallelujah&quot; became Buckley&#39;s first number one on Billboard&#39;s Hot Digital Songs and reached number two in the UK singles chart. In 2014, &quot;Hallelujah&quot; was inducted into the American Library of Congress&#39; National Recording Registry.</p><p><br></p>",
